    "Both stations need to be served by the same transit network. Try picking stations that share a metro, tram or bus line." : {
      "comment" : "A description of the error that occurs when the start and end stations of a ticket are not in the same public transport network.",
      "isCommentAutoGenerated" : true,
      "localizations" : {
        "de" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Beide Stationen müssen vom selben Verkehrsnetz bedient werden. Bitte wählen Sie Stationen, die über eine gemeinsame U-Bahn-, Tram- oder Buslinie erreichbar sind."
          }
        },
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Both stations need to be served by the same transit network. Try picking stations that share a metro, tram or bus line."
          }
        },
        "es" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Ambas estaciones deben pertenecer a la misma red de transporte. Pruebe con estaciones que compartan una línea de metro, tranvía o autobús."
          }
        },
        "fr" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Les deux stations doivent appartenir au même réseau de transport. Choisissez des stations partageant la même ligne de métro, de tram ou de bus."
          }
        },
        "it" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Entrambe le stazioni devono appartenere alla stessa rete di trasporto. Scelga stazioni che condividano una linea di metro, tram o autobus."
          }
        },
        "ja" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "両方の駅が同じ交通ネットワークに属している必要があります。同じ地下鉄・路面電車・バス路線が通っている駅をお選びください。"
          }
        },
        "ko" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "두 정거장이 같은 교통망에 속해 있어야 합니다. 같은 지하철·트램·버스 노선이 지나는 정거장을 선택해 주세요."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "两个站点需位于同一交通网络。请选择共享地铁、有轨电车或公交线路的站点。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
