    "You both benefit from an extra memory slot. Need more? Upgrade to Lumoria Premium and create unlimited memories." : {
      "comment" : "A description of the benefits of upgrading to Lumoria Premium.",
      "isCommentAutoGenerated" : true,
      "localizations" : {
        "de" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Ihr habt beide einen zusätzlichen Erinnerungsplatz bekommen. Willst du mehr? Mit Lumoria Premium gibt’s unbegrenzte Erinnerungen."
          }
        },
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "You both got an extra memory slot. Want more? Lumoria Premium unlocks unlimited memories."
          }
        },
        "es" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Ambos conseguisteis una memoria extra. ¿Quieres más? Lumoria Premium desbloquea memorias ilimitadas."
          }
        },
        "fr" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Vous avez tous les deux gagné un souvenir de plus. Vous en voulez davantage ? Lumoria Premium débloque des souvenirs illimités."
          }
        },
        "it" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Avete ottenuto entrambi un ricordo in più. Ne vuoi altri? Lumoria Premium sblocca ricordi illimitati."
          }
        },
        "ja" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "おふたりにメモリー枠がひとつ追加されました。もっと増やしたい方は、Lumoria Premium で無制限に。"
          }
        },
        "ko" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "두 분 모두 추억 슬롯이 하나 늘었어요. 더 원하신다면 Lumoria Premium에서 무제한으로 풀립니다."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "你们俩都多获得了一个回忆位。想要更多？Lumoria Premium 解锁无限回忆。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "You can log back in anytime with the same email." : {
      "comment" : "Confirmation dialog body.",
      "localizations" : {
        "de" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Du kannst dich jederzeit mit derselben E-Mail wieder anmelden."
          }
        },
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "You can log back in anytime with the same email."
          }
        },
        "es" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Puedes volver a iniciar sesión cuando quieras con el mismo correo."
          }
        },
        "fr" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Vous pouvez vous reconnecter à tout moment avec la même adresse e-mail."
          }
        },
        "it" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Puoi rientrare quando vuoi con la stessa email."
          }
        },
        "ja" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "同じメールアドレスでいつでも再度サインインできます。"
          }
        },
        "ko" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "같은 이메일로 언제든 다시 로그인할 수 있어요."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "您随时可以用同一个邮箱重新登录。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "You can now enjoy Lumoria and create beautiful tickets for every moments you'd like to remember. We just covered the basics of Lumoria. There's so many more features waiting to be discovered." : {
      "comment" : "A description of the features of Lumoria.",
      "isCommentAutoGenerated" : true,
      "localizations" : {
        "de" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Jetzt können Sie Lumoria nutzen und schöne Tickets für jeden Moment erstellen, an den Sie sich erinnern möchten. Das waren erst die Grundlagen – es warten noch viele weitere Funktionen auf Sie."
          }
        },
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "You can now enjoy Lumoria and create beautiful tickets for every moments you'd like to remember. We just covered the basics of Lumoria. There's so many more features waiting to be discovered."
          }
        },
        "es" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Ya puede disfrutar de Lumoria y crear boletos preciosos para cada momento que quiera recordar. Acabamos de ver lo básico; hay muchas más funciones esperando a ser descubiertas."
          }
        },
        "fr" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Vous pouvez désormais profiter de Lumoria et créer de beaux billets pour chaque moment que vous souhaitez garder en mémoire. Nous venons de couvrir les bases : de nombreuses autres fonctionnalités vous attendent."
          }
        },
        "it" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Ora può usare Lumoria e creare bellissimi biglietti per ogni momento che vuole ricordare. Abbiamo visto solo le basi: molte altre funzioni la aspettano."
          }
        },
        "ja" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "これで Lumoria をお使いいただけます。残しておきたい瞬間ごとに美しいチケットを作成しましょう。今ご案内したのは基本だけ。まだまだ多くの機能が待っています。"
          }
        },
        "ko" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "이제 Lumoria로 간직하고 싶은 모든 순간을 위한 멋진 티켓을 만들어 보세요. 지금까지는 기본만 살펴봤습니다. 아직 많은 기능이 여러분을 기다리고 있어요."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "现在您可以开始使用 Lumoria,为每一个想要珍藏的瞬间创建精美票券。我们刚刚介绍的只是基础,还有更多功能等您发现。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "You can replay it anytime from Settings." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "de" : {
